{"id":17537,"date":"2014-01-09T15:36:23","date_gmt":"2014-01-09T11:36:23","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=17537"},"modified":"2025-04-09T12:51:38","modified_gmt":"2025-04-09T08:51:38","slug":"tasbih-tahmid-33-times","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/tasbih-tahmid-33-times\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Salat: Glorify Allah 33 times after every prayer"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: The poor emigrants came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cThe wealthy have taken the highest degrees and blessed ranks!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>How is that<\/strong>?\u201d They said, \u201cThey pray as we pray, they fast as we fast, they give in charity but we do not have charity to give, they free slaves but we have none to free.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Shall I teach you something by which you will catch up to those ahead of you, surpass those who had outraced you, and no one will be better than you but one who acts like you<\/b>?\u201d They said, \u201cOf course, O Messenger of Allah!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Glorify Allah, exalt Allah, and praise Allah thirty-three times after every prayer<\/b>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 843, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 595<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <b><i>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/i><\/b>\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0641\u064f\u0642\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0647\u064e\u0627\u062c\u0650\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0